As you may know, one of the key developments the Norman King made was the

00:07:46.872 --> 00:07:52.652
creation of a central system of law and order, with the king at its centre.

00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:58.710
Under William the Conqueror, a crime was no longer just an offence against

