00:22:51.734 --> 00:22:55.844
So, by the mid-19th century, Britain was still grappling with a

00:22:55.844 --> 00:23:00.244
fundamental question: what was the purpose of a criminal sentence?

00:23:01.024 --> 00:23:06.374
